    <h1 class="text-2xl font-semibold">
        <Petapetual /> for dearly departed relatives
    </h1>

    <p>
        There’s truly no easy way to navigate the loss of a family member. It’s
        a deeply personal, profound, and tremendously emotional experience that
        can leave you feeling adrift. The world feels quieter, and the space
        they once filled feels impossibly large.
    </p>

    <p>
        In the midst of that sorrow, a powerful need often surfaces: the desire
        to remember them, honour them, and pay respects to them. We find
        ourselves wanting to gather the fragments of their life, the happy
        memories, the funny stories, and the photos that capture their smile
        <i>just right</i>. We want to celebrate the beautiful, complex life they
        lived.
    </p>

    <p>
        This is a fundamental part of grieving and remembering. It’s the need
        for a place to put that love and a way to share it with others who are
        also feeling the loss.
    </p>

    <p>
        At <Petapetual />, we understand that need deeply. We created our online
        memorials to offer a peaceful, permanent space where you can build a
        beautiful tribute to your loved one. It’s a place to collect those
        cherished photos, write down those precious stories, and invite family
        and friends from all over the world to share their own memories. It
        allows their light to keep shining and provides a central place for
        comfort, reflection, and celebration, ensuring their legacy is preserved
        for generations to come.
    </p>
</DefaultPageLayout>
